Package: STMFaultPattern
Title: Manage virtual wafer of good and faulty chips
Version: 1.2
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Emanuele", family = "Fabbiani", email = "donlelef@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")), person( given = "Claudio", family = "Peroni", role = "aut"))
Description: This package lets you fill a square matrix where each element
    is assumed to represent a chip an a wafer. To better simulate real wafer, it
    provedes a function to force the elements out of a circle to a given value.
    Functions are provided to switch from absolute coordinates to matrix indexes.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.3)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
